text: Cieślak () is a Polish surname, it may refer to: * Bronisław Cieślak (born 1943), Polish actor and politician * Jadwiga Jankowska-Cieślak (born 1951), Polish actress * Marek Cieślak (born 1950), Polish speedway rider * Michał Cieślak (born 1968), Polish rower * Włodzimierz Cieślak (born 1950), Polish wrestler Category:Polish-language surnames
